
                        Welcome to PDCurses

 Contents
 --------
 This directory contains core PDCurses source code files specific to
 the Win32 platform - console mode (NT and Window 95).


 Distribution Status
 -------------------

 The files in this directory are released to the Public Domain.


 Acknowlegements
 ---------------

